3:
The bodies of their dead will be thrown out. The stench of the dead bodies will be everywhere;
\q1 and the mountains will soak up their blood.
\q1

5:
For when my sword will have drunk its fill in heaven;
\q1 look, it will now come down on Edom, on the people I am setting apart for destruction.
\q1

10:
It will burn night and day; its smoke will rise forever;
\q1 from generation to generation it will
be a wasteland; no one will pass through it forever and ever.
